<subSubSection id="C31D6540FF9ABD16FD4EF5DBFCF2F488" pageId="6" pageNumber="135" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8BB836CBFF9ABD16FD4EF5DBFCF2F488" blockId="6.[680,1304,2581,3008]" pageId="6" pageNumber="135">
Classically treated as a member of the subgenus 
<taxonomicName id="4C074D48FF9ABD16FCAAF533FC3FF507" box="[813,932,2700,2733]" class="Mammalia" family="Spalacidae" genus="Rhizomys" kingdom="Animalia" order="Rodentia" pageId="6" pageNumber="135" phylum="Chordata" rank="genus">Rhizomys</taxonomicName>
. Distributions of subspecies are poorly delineated, and multiple species may be present. Five subspecies recognized.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
